McMath was declared brain dead following a tonsil surgery intended to help the girl's sleep apnea on December 9.

Following the surgery, the girl suffered tremendous blood loss and went into cardiac arrest. The poor circulation as a result of the severe blood loss caused injuries to her brain that doctors considered to be fatal.

